USUN TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 50.14% to NT$88,292,000 from NT$177,097,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales             88,292          177,097    
YOY%             -50.14%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            278,405          482,844    
YOY%             -42.34% 
=================================================================
 